OL,3,CTeenager accused of raping girl, 13,
OL,4,Ctells jury she 'asked him for sex'
OL,6,FA teenager has denied raping a 13-year-
OL,7,Fold girl in bushes near a tram stop,
OL,8,Ftelling a jury that she had "asked him
OL,9,Ffor sex".
OL,11,FThe boy is one of three boys, who
OL,12,Fcannot be named, who are alleged to
OL,13,Fhave raped the girl when they were 12,
OL,14,F13 and 14.
OL,16,FThe teenage girl, who also cannot be
OL,17,Fnamed, was allegedly attacked just off
OL,18,Fa footpath near the Newbold tram stop
OL,19,Fin Rochdale in February 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
