PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773331878
OL,3,CTeenager accused of raping girl, 13,
OL,4,Ctells jury she 'asked him for sex'
OL,6,FThe three boys deny the charges they
OL,7,Fface. Two, now aged 15 and 16, are
OL,8,Fstanding trial at Manchester's
OL,9,FMinshull Street Crown Court. The
OL,10,Fthird, who is now 14, has been deemed
OL,11,Funfit to stand trial, jurors were told
OL,12,Fas the case was opened.
OL,14,FGiving evidence, the now 15-year-old
OL,15,Fsaid on the date of the incident, he
OL,16,Fhad been out in Rochdale town centre
OL,17,Fwith the two co-accused.
OL,19,F"We hang out around town and have
OL,20,Fbanter around town," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
