OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773331878
OL,3,CTeenager accused of raping girl, 13,
OL,4,Ctells jury she 'asked him for sex'
OL,6,FQuestioned by his barrister, Peter
OL,7,FGilmour, about CCTV footage that
OL,8,Fshowed him running around the town
OL,9,Fcentre, he said: "We were running
OL,10,Faround, having some races. I was 13
OL,11,Fand that's what we used to do. We used
OL,12,Fto run around quite a lot back then."
OL,14,FThe boy said he saw the alleged victim
OL,15,Fin the town centre and said he
OL,16,Fbelieved she was older, looking
OL,17,F'fifteen or sixteen'. Asked why he
OL,18,Fthought she looked older he said:
OL,19,F"Because the way they (the alleged
OL,20,Fvictim and her friend) were dressed
OL,21,Fand constantly smoking vapes".
OL,26,@{D@Wpm|D@Vpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
