CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773331878
OL,3,CTeenager accused of raping girl, 13,
OL,4,Ctells jury she 'asked him for sex'
OL,6,FLater that afternoon, after
OL,7,Fencountering some youngsters at
OL,8,FRochdale tram stop, he said he saw the
OL,9,Fgirl there with some friends.
OL,11,FAsked if there was anything about her
OL,12,Fhe noticed, he said: "I could tell the
OL,13,Fway she was looking at me, she fancied
OL,14,Fme."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
