PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773331878
OL,3,CTeenager accused of raping girl, 13,
OL,4,Ctells jury she 'asked him for sex'
OL,6,FAsked by Mr Gilmour to elaborate, he
OL,7,Fadded: "We were at the tram stop and
OL,8,Fwe were showing off a little bit. I
OL,9,Fcould tell the way she was looking at
OL,10,Fme, she fancied me. She was just
OL,11,Fconstantly looking at me, she looked
OL,12,Fhappy."
OL,14,FThey boarded the same tram and the boy
OL,15,Fsaid there "was a bit of flirting and
OL,16,Flaughing" on the journey.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
