PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773331878
OL,3,CTeenager accused of raping girl, 13,
OL,4,Ctells jury she 'asked him for sex'
OL,6,FGiving evidence about the conversation
OL,7,Fduring the tram ride, he said: "I
OL,8,Fasked how old she was and she asked
OL,9,Fhow old I was. We said we were 13. I
OL,10,Fheard (her) saying to (her friend) she
OL,11,Ffancies me.
OL,13,F"There was some talk about sex on the
OL,14,Ftram. (She) said she wanted to have
OL,15,Fsex with me. She was saying it to (her
OL,16,Ffriend). The lads told me that."
OL,18,FHe said they all got off the tram at
OL,19,FNewbold and he put his arm around the
OL,20,Fgirl.
OL,26,@rD@GpmrD@KpnrD@WpmrD@bpnvD@GpmvD@KpnwD@
OL,26,AcpmxD@Gpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
