PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773331878
OL,3,CTeenager accused of raping girl, 13,
OL,4,Ctells jury she 'asked him for sex'
OL,6,F"She did not object to that. She was
OL,7,Fsmiling, I thought she was
OL,8,Fcomfortable," he said.
OL,10,FThe now 15-year-old say they initially
OL,11,Fwent into the bush and claimed the
OL,12,Fgirl said she wanted to have sex with
OL,13,Fhim.
OL,15,F"Did you want to do that?" Mr Gilmour
OL,16,Fasked.
OL,18,F"Yes," the boy replied.
OL,20,F"Was anything said about condoms?" the
OL,21,Fbarrister asked.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
