PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773331878
OL,3,CTeenager accused of raping girl, 13,
OL,4,Ctells jury she 'asked him for sex'
OL,6,F"Yes, I asked (her) for sex, she said
OL,7,Fwe needed condoms and I said I didn't
OL,8,Fneed them."
OL,10,FThe boy said he had never had sex
OL,11,Fbefore and didn't know how to use a
OL,12,Fcondom.
OL,14,F"Why did you say you didn't need a
OL,15,Fcondom?" Mr Gilmour asked.
OL,17,F"Because I wouldn't need to have a
OL,18,Fcondom to have sex," the boy replied.
OL,26,@nD@OpmnD@Spn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
