CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773331878
OL,3,CTeenager accused of raping girl, 13,
OL,4,Ctells jury she 'asked him for sex'
OL,6,FHe said they then walked back into the
OL,7,Fbush, stating the girl went first,
OL,8,Ffollowed by the three boys. He denied
OL,9,Fpushing or dragging her into the bush.
OL,11,FThe boy claimed he saw the girl
OL,12,Fperforming oral sex on the now 14-year-
OL,13,Fold. He also said he recorded a 10-
OL,14,Fsecond video which showed the girl
OL,15,Fperforming oral sex on him whilst the
OL,16,Fnow 16-year-old boy was behind her.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
