PN,39210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773331878
OL,3,CTeenager accused of raping girl, 13,
OL,4,Ctells jury she 'asked him for sex'
OL,6,F"Did you know what (the now 16-year-
OL,7,Fold) was doing?" Mr Gilmour asked. "He
OL,8,Fwas having sex with her," the boy
OL,9,Fsaid. The now 15-year-old said he had
OL,10,Ftold the girl to 's*** it'.
OL,12,FAsked why he decided to film the
OL,13,Fencounter, he said: "Because at the
OL,14,Ftime I used to film everything I did.
OL,15,FI thought it was OK to film her."
OL,17,FAsked if he thought what he was doing
OL,18,Fwas wrong, he said no. He said he sent
OL,19,Fthe video to the now 16-year-old
OL,20,F'because he asked him to'.
OL,26,@nD@TpmoD@Dpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
