PN,39211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773331878
OL,3,CTeenager accused of raping girl, 13,
OL,4,Ctells jury she 'asked him for sex'
OL,6,FAsked why he left the bush, he said:
OL,7,F"I left because I wasn't h**d and I
OL,8,Fcouldn't do anything and my mates were
OL,9,Fgoing. I just followed them," he said.
OL,11,FWhen questioned why he ran from the
OL,12,Fbushes, he said: "You can see us
OL,13,Frunning around town all day, that's
OL,14,Fwhat we were doing."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
