PN,39212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773331878
OL,3,CTeenager accused of raping girl, 13,
OL,4,Ctells jury she 'asked him for sex'
OL,6,FMr Gilmour asked how he felt about the
OL,7,Fincident. he said: "It doesn't make me
OL,8,Ffeel very good, that these people are
OL,9,Fsaying these false allegations. And my
OL,10,Ffamily have gone through a lot of
OL,11,Fstress about it. It's just not been
OL,12,Fnice seeing my family stressed."
OL,14,FHe added: "I don't feel very happy
OL,15,Fabout what happened."
OL,17,FThe boy previously told the court that
OL,18,Fhe left school early and worked for
OL,19,Fhis family's business.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
