PN,39213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773331878
OL,3,CTeenager accused of raping girl, 13,
OL,4,Ctells jury she 'asked him for sex'
OL,6,FThe trial has previously been told how
OL,7,Fthe boys "took it in turns and swapped
OL,8,Fpositions" during the incident in
OL,9,FFebruary 2024.
OL,11,FProsecutors say part of the alleged
OL,12,Fattack on the then-13-year-old was
OL,13,Ffilmed on a mobile phone and was later
OL,14,F"circulated amongst themselves" and
OL,15,F"others".
OL,17,FPreviously, Ms Whittlestone said the
OL,18,Fnow 14-year-old has been found unfit
OL,19,Fto stand trial.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
