FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773331878
OL,3,CTeenager accused of raping girl, 13,
OL,4,Ctells jury she 'asked him for sex'
OL,6,FShe said the jury would be asked to
OL,7,Ffind "whether he did the act" and
OL,8,Fwhether he "encouraged" it to happen
OL,9,Fwithout the girl's consent.
OL,11,FThe indictment contains five counts of
OL,12,Frape. Three counts relate specifically
OL,13,Fto each boy, while two are charged as
OL,14,F'joint enterprise', jurors were told.
OL,15,FEach boy denies the charges they face.
OL,17,FThe trial continues.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/14
